quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  5,83,"Si …ďe nanii ko Jippinaa kon e Nulaa…óo on, a yi'ay gite ma…ď…ďe …óen no yuppoo gon…ói, sabu kon ko …ďe anndi e goonga kan. He…ďe mbia: "Joom amen, min gooŇč…óinii, Winndidu min e seedii…ďe …ďen"."
  5,84,"E ko ha…óata amen gooŇč…óinde Alla e ko ari e amen kon immorde e goonga, men tam∆īinoo nde Joomi amen Wa…ótida men e yim…ďe mo∆ī∆īu…ďe …ďeen?"."
  5,85,"Alla Yo…ďiri …ďe sabu kon ko …ďe mbi'i : Aljannaaji …ói caatli ilata senngo ley majji, ko …ďe duumotoo…ďe ton. ∆äum …óon ko njo…ďdi mo∆ī∆īin…ďe …ďe,"
  5,86,"∆Āeen heefer…ďe …ďe njeddi Aayeeje amen …óeen, …ďeen …óoon, ko yim…ďe Jahiimi."
  5,87,"Eehey mon yo gooŇč…óin…ďe, wota on karrmin laa…ďu…ói …ói Alla dakginani on, wata on njatu. Pe keerol, Alla Yi…óaa yawtoo…ďe …ďn.keeri Alla"
  5,88,"√Ďaamee e kon ko Alla Arsiki on dagii…ói laa…ďu…ói. Kulon Alla O Mo ngooŇč…óin…óon."
  5,89,"Alla Nanngitirtaa on ko falju…óon ka goo…óndooje mon, kono Homo Nanngitira on kon ko pi…ď…óon e goo…óndoodooje …óe e muu…óum. Kaffaara mum on, ko √Īammingol miskinee…ďe sappo immorde ko hakindii e ko √Īamminton …ďeynguureeji mon, maa koltu ma…ď…ďe, maa rim…óin gol daande. On mo he…ďaali […óuum], ko koorgol …ďal…óe tati. ∆äuum …óoon ko kaffaara goo…óndooje mon si on ngoo…óndii. Ndeenee goo…óndooje mon …óe .Ko nii Alla ∆Āannginiranta on Aayeeje Makko …óen, belajo'o, on njetta [Mo]."